<refsection>
	<title>Description</title>
	<para>
		Read a message in RFC 822 format from the standard input and send it to the server. Newsgroups can be specified
in two manners:
		<itemizedlist>
			<listitem><para>as a command-line arguments,</para></listitem>
			<listitem><para>in the Newsgroups header of the message.</para></listitem>
		</itemizedlist>
		The latter method takes precedence over command-line arguments. Read message can be altered by the specified
plugins which are described along with global options in
		<citerefentry>
			<refentrytitle>sinntp</refentrytitle>
			<manvolnum>1</manvolnum>
		</citerefentry>.
	</para>
</refsection>

